6{z_<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";s:403:"I went to the Giang Vo location for a pelvic exam and consultation. The ladies in there were so lovely and warm and I had an English speaking nurse with me explaining everything. I was super emotional the whole time because I'm hormonal and was a bit worried and they were so good with me- holding my hands, giving me advice. I would HIGHLY recommend Marie Stopes Clinic for all your sexual health needs";}